textAfterTable: Profile iShares FTSE MIB UCITS ETF (Dist) is an open-end, UCITS compliant exchange traded fund incorporated in Ireland. The Fund aims to track the performance of the FTSE MIB Index. The FTSE MIB Index offers exposure to the 40 largest and most liquid Italian stocks listed on Borsa Italiana. The fund distributes income received to shareholders.
